originalText.text:
Alison is an extraordinary human being and spirit.

The last four years have been a life changing movement in my life, removing the things that have once held me back. Over the last year or so, however, there were reminders that I need to remain steadfast in this journey to live the most healthy, happy and loving life I can. What Alison did for me in our first few sessions has been nothing short of absolutely breathtaking. She has provided me guidance as my spirit guides were recounting the past and how best to honor all parts of myself whilst holding my love, strength, wisdom and care in paramount regard so I can share to whomever, wherever, whenever.

To say I recommend would be an understatement and then some. Thank you for all you do Alison, you truly have made this journey incredibly better.
